text:
Pehla banda jisse mulakat hui poore iit m. Pehli din tu bilkul chup tha, meri mummy kehti h kitna seedha ladka h Gaurav (Unhe kon bataye ab). Teri wajah se aaj bhi kursi pe kuch rakh ke sona padhta h.
Kaafi maje dilaye tune 4 saal m. Dhanyawad. Bas itna hi.
